<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Heteropterys from the Parabanisteria group from the State of Goias, Brazil A H. byrsonimifolia B H. coriacea C H. eglandulosa D H. escalloniifolia E H. nervosa F H. pannosa G H. procoriacea H H. rosmarinifolia. A by L. C. Marinho B, G by I. Morais C, H by R. Sartin D, E by R. F. Almeida F by R. Ripley." , "Figure 2. Holotype of Heteropterys rosmarinifolia R. F. Almeida & M. Pell. (R. Sartin et al. 576, UFRN barcode 00024927)." , "Figure 1. Heteropterys rosmarinifolia R. F. Almeida & M. Pell. A savannah grasslands from Reserva Natural Serra do Tombador B habit C detail of the apex of the branch, showing the verticillate leaves and solitary inflorescence D cincinnus, showing the concave bracteoles and the floral bud E front view of the flower. All photos by R. Sartin, except A by H. Palo-Jr." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/521716" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/521715" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/521714" .

